org.fujion.client

Class ExecutionContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fujion.client.ExecutionContext

  • public class ExecutionContext
extends Object
    Static helper class for threads to determine the current execution context. An execution context is created each time a thread services a client request. It contains information about the target page and the session servicing the request, as well as the request itself.
